ConstValues.value: "Hi there, I would like to request a new feature for the application. It would be great to have an option to customize the app's theme colors. This would allow users to personalize the look and feel of the interface according to their preferences. The customization could include primary, secondary, and accent colors. Please consider adding this feature in the next update. Thank you!"
